City Court of New York — General Term, January, 1901.

Before Fitzsimons, Oh. J., O’Dwyer and Hascall, JJ.

Mike Lakner, Respondent, v. Julia M. Goggill et al., Appellants. Appeal by defendant Fried from a judgment of the City Court of the City of New York, in favor of plaintiff. Joseph I. Green, for appellants; Albert I. Sire, for respondent.

Judgment affirmed, with costs. No opinion.
